"title": "5831: depression",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5831: depression",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A deep sense of despondency, discouragement and sadness, often linked with a sense of personal powerlessness and a loss of meaning in and enthusiasm for life. Many biblical characters show evidence of such behaviour which originates in a number of different ways.</p>\n<h2>Some causes of depression</h2>\n<h3>External circumstances</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:8\">2CO 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3-1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:3–19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:23\">JOB 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:1-Ps42:11\">PSA 42:1–42:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:1-Ps88:18\">PSA 88:1–88:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:11\">JOL 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Physical illness or exhaustion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:5-1Kgs19:8\">1KI 19:5–19:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:15-Gen21:16\">GEN 21:15–21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:1-Ps6:7\">PSA 6:1–6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:14-Ps22:17\">PSA 22:14–22:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:9-Ps31:12\">PSA 31:9–31:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:1-Isa38:2\">ISA 38:1–38:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:5\">JON 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>Fear of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:1-1Kgs19:3\">1KI 19:1–19:3</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Fear of failure</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:1\">EXO 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:11-Num11:15\">NUM 11:11–11:15</a></p>\n<h3>Serious sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:3-Matt27:4\">MAT 27:3–27:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:16-Ps25:18\">PSA 25:16–25:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:2-Jer14:3\">JER 14:2–14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:7\">JER 14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:9-Jer16:10\">JER 16:9–16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:16-Ezek4:17\">EZK 4:16–4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:26-Ezek7:27\">EZK 7:26–7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:19\">EZK 12:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:10-Rev16:11\">REV 16:10–16:11</a></p>\n<h3>A sense of the futility of life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:17-Eccl2:20\">ECC 2:17–2:20</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Loss of sense of God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1-Ps22:2\">PSA 22:1–22:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:46\">MAT 27:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:34\">MRK 15:34</a></p>\n<h2>Symptoms of depression</h2>\n<h3>A loathing of life and a desire to end it</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:15\">NUM 11:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:1\">JOB 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:17\">ECC 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:15-Jer20:18\">JER 20:15–20:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:8\">JON 4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Deep sorrow</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:16\">GEN 21:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg21:2\">JDG 21:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:10\">1SA 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:16\">1SA 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:3\">PSA 42:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:4\">NEH 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:2\">NEH 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:1-Esth4:3\">EST 4:1–4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:16\">JOB 16:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:11\">LAM 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>Loneliness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:10\">1KI 19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:14\">NUM 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:14\">1KI 19:14</a></p>\n<h3>Perplexity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:5\">PSA 42:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:2\">HAB 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:17\">LUK 24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:6\">JHN 16:6</a></p>\n<h3>Despair</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:1\">JOB 17:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:3-Ps88:9\">PSA 88:3–88:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:8-2Cor1:9\">2CO 1:8–1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Escapism</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:6-Ps55:8\">PSA 55:6–55:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:1-1Kgs19:3\">1KI 19:1–19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:22\">JER 8:22</a></p>\n<h3>Feeling forsaken by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1\">PSA 22:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:9\">PSA 27:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:21\">PSA 38:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:14\">ISA 49:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:18\">JER 15:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:1-Lam3:20\">LAM 3:1–3:20</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of spiritual depression</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:13\">JDG 6:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:9-1Kgs19:18\">1KI 19:9–19:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1-Ps22:2\">PSA 22:1–22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:6-Ps22:8\">PSA 22:6–22:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:1-Ps42:7\">PSA 42:1–42:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:9-Ps42:11\">PSA 42:9–42:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:1-Ps43:5\">PSA 43:1–43:5</a></p>\n<h2>Remedies for depression</h2>\n<h3>Renewed vision of God and being centred upon him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:11\">1KI 19:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:3\">ISA 26:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:7-Jer17:8\">JER 17:7–17:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:6\">ROM 8:6</a></p>\n<h3>Hope and trust in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:11\">PSA 42:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:9-Ps22:11\">PSA 22:9–22:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:22-Ps22:31\">PSA 22:22–22:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:16-Hab3:18\">HAB 3:16–3:18</a></p>\n<h3>Praise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:1\">PSA 30:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:5\">PSA 42:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:1-Ps107:43\">PSA 107:1–107:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:3\">ISA 61:1–61:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:8-2Cor4:12\">2CO 4:8–4:12</a></p>\n<h3>Reviewing what God has done</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:11-Ps77:12\">PSA 77:11–77:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:6\">PSA 42:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:5\">PSA 143:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:19-Lam3:26\">LAM 3:19–3:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:6\">2CO 7:6</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6-Phil4:7\">PHP 4:6–4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:23\">PSA 139:23</a></p>",
